      <p>
        This website is private, and it was created solely to display my
        writings, projects, and personal things that are interesting to me;
        therefore, the quality of this website is subjective only to me. If you
        have any suggestions on how this website can be improved, or if you find
        any:
      </p>
      <ul id="contact-ul">
        <li style="margin: var(--in-page-li-spacing) 0">wrong information,</li>
        <li style="margin: var(--in-page-li-spacing) 0">
          errors in the source code,
        </li>
        <li style="margin: var(--in-page-li-spacing) 0">
          contents that you are not happy about,
        </li>
        <li style="margin: var(--in-page-li-spacing) 0">
          spelling or grammar errors,
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        feel free to reach out to me using the email address below. Any feedback
