      </p>
      <p>
        I am also open for conversations, so if you just want to have a chat,
        you can reach out to me via
        <a href="https://discordapp.com/users/750019342518714398" class="url"
          >discord</a
        >
        or <a href="https://t.me/doodle_04" class="url">telegram</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

